sktok_condtr.desc_en:
When activated during a variation, enables switching between <@gold>passionate</> and <@purple>melancholic</> variations, and gives allies a buff for <@ba.vup>20s</>:
When passionate variation is active, ASPD <@ba.vup>+50</>;
when melancholic variation is active, ATK <@ba.vup>+60%</> but ASPD <@ba.vup>-10</>;
for every Tuning Node on the battlefield, <@ba.vup>gain</> 1 additional stack
